00210 void
00211 Triple<T1, T2, T3>::parse(std::istream& is)
00212 {
00213         // force parsing as integer instead of a single character
00214         if (sizeof_T1 == sizeof_int8_t) is >> tmp_int, e1_ = tmp_int;
00215         else is >> e1_;
00216 
00217         if (sizeof_T2 == sizeof_int8_t) is >> tmp_int, e2_ = tmp_int;
00218         else is >> e2_;
00219 
00220         if (sizeof_T3 == sizeof_int8_t) is >> tmp_int, e3_ = tmp_int;
00221         else is >> e3_;
00222 }
